getStyle

public int getStyle()
Returns the style of the SOAP payload.

setStyle

public void setStyle(int newStyle)
              throws WSDLException
Sets the style of the SOAP payload. It is either RPC or Document. The legal values are SOAPBinding.RPC or SOAPBinding.DOCUMENT.

The default is SOAPBinding.DOCUMENT.

Parameters:
newStyle - int representing the style of the SOAP payload
Throws:
WSDLException - if the style is invalid.
